title: Computer Science M.S. - Western Washington University
description: Completing a Master's of Science in Computer Science at Western Washington University with a focus in machine learning research under Dr. Brian Hutchinson. Developed machine learning solutions to real world problems in bioinformatics.

title: Computer Science B.S. - Western Washington University
description: Completed a Bachelor's of Science in Computer Science at Western Washington University with minors in both Mathematics and Physics.
